values:
sun sun sun
way too much sun.

dont look up
your eyes might boil.

is it just me
or is it BOILING?

you and I must both
be this sweaty.

IT IS SO HOT
HOT HOT HOT.

being this hot
does not seem possible

please tell me
you brought sun screen

so so so so so
so so so hot

okay,
being this hot is not normal
